Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Mark City auction’s grand finale treasure turned out\Nto be a Tier 7 pill, Yin-Yang Mysterious Dragon Pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,While everybody was vying for this divine pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan, knowing that he was cash-strapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,left after taking his auction earnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The final winner of the divine pill, Sky Serpent Mansion’s Elder Qing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was met with the Blood Sect’s ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan, who had been trailing Fan Ling, unexpectedly witnessed this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve been waiting for you for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You came for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What secret does this map hold, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,can’t tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-star Fight Grandmaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,daring to walk into a trap with such little strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you sure have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Sect Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,why must you handle it personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand by;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in case he plans to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What great strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But fortunately, this fellow is only at the Fight Grandmaster level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a Fight Spirit practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does this fellow’s Dou Qi have a kind of tenuous feeling to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,today, you no longer have half a thread’s chance for regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to thank you for bringing me good news\Nthat the map indeed contains a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t have you end up a shriveled corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone Disintegrating Evil Blood Palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unexpected that the Sect Leader passed down\Nthis level of Fight Technique to Junior Sect Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He really does have high expectations for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with your current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you are still no match for a Fight Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That may not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,are you thinking of‒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Fire Three Mysterious Change, First Change:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Lotus Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he actually possesses a Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Sect Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,our Blood Sect is the most suppressed by Heavenly Flame;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it is best for us to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Delay him a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as my father arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,originally I wanted to leave it for Ling’er.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My father Fan Lao is a Fight Emperor;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t mess around, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to stall until Fan Lao gets here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Sect Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hold him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you must make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan, hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually‒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,fell‒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sky Fire Three Mysterious Change,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,its power is quite great;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the toll it takes on the body isn’t small either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ve improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the first time you used Sky Fire Three Mysterious Change,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you were barely able to hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve detected Fan Lao’s aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ling’er.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make them suffer the pain of having their\Nflesh torn apart by ten thousand blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer perceive Fan Lao’s aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s rest overnight before departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow’s luck is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In little more than three years, you’ve\Nobtained three map fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are again one step closer to the\NPurifying Demonic Lotus Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all thanks to Teacher’s insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else, no matter how lucky I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look at this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Consume it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving it on you isn’t safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,take this Yin-Yang Mysterious Dragon Pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is but a Tier 7 pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,consume it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing isn’t fake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn’t there the slightest reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of reaction do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like the pills you took in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,having to go through excruciating pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Tier 7 pill, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There has got to be some baseline effect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At that auction, didn’t they say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that this pill’s main effect is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“stand after breaking.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the medicinal strength enters the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you will naturally be able to manifest unimaginable\Nbenefits in a life-and-death situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this sort of opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can only occur once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of inhuman torture isn’t something just anyone can bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Feng Xian with his tenacious temperament
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was almost unable to hang on back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain that even a Fight Ancestor would find difficult to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher is familiar with Venerate Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will gradually tell you more about myself in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing too much right now will not benefit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,does this pill not have the slightest use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This Mysterious Dragon Pill was refined\Nfrom Rank 6 Dragon-type Monster Cores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If by chance you were to absorb some\Nof the thin dragon aura it contains,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with use of a compatible Sonic Fight Technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when facing enemies in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be a trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try circulating your Dou Qi to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,inheritance succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat sure has enough luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you have indeed inherited that soul-shocking strange dragon aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with your current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just relying on the dragon aura to make sonic waves\Nis far too damaging to your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You must pair it with a Sonic Fight Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,those kinds of Fight Techniques are quite rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to obtain one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to inherit the dragon aura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is already an unexpected gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As for a Sonic Fight Technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll just look for one in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be very familiar with this\NYin-Yang Mysterious Dragon Pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,actually knowing how to drive out the hidden dragon aura inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are you‒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That Yin-Yang Mysterious Dragon Pill’s medicinal formula
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was created by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people on the Continent who can refine it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,consist of two individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One is myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the other
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is my student whom I once regarded as the most perfect inheritor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was still a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I carried him out from icy cold debris
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and raised him like my own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His talent in alchemy was not any lesser than yours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and he eventually became a most outstanding alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,due to some things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he chose to betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How I am today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is all thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I later met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn’t have left Black Mark City this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps he personally delivered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we were really able to find him at Black Mark City, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of constrainment by that Hall of Souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not dare to appear at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just based on your current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whether in terms of alchemy or Dou Qi cultivation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you are no match for him by a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will surpass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I will clean up the sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will not be blind a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Yao Chen, also believe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that these old eyes of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will certainly not be blind a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to Jia Nan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The earlier we find the Fallen Heart Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the earlier I can refine a body for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jia Nan Academy’s old fellows aren't pushovers, mind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By then, I won’t be able to come out freely;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you will only be able to rely on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher shouldn’t underestimate me;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,among people around my age,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t need you to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I was‒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Up ahead is Jia Nan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot forcefully fly within one hundred miles of Jia Nan Academy;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise, you will draw attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will enter through Peace Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jia Nan Academy really is powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,pressuring even Black Corner Region’s people into submissive obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the terrifying Death Spirit Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter Peace Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you must consume this pill specially refined\Nby the Academy for sensing killing intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you possess murderous intentions while in the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your whole body will suffuse with red light
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you’ll be wanted for arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Before leaving the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,just go to the antidote distribution site to receive the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,can Academy students
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,be exempt from taking the pill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You claim you are an Academy student;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,report your name, age and recruitment instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Instructor Ruo Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are that Xiao Yan from Jia Ma Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who requested two years’ leave of absence in one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So it’s actually him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he’s just so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like this girl’s reputation in the Academy isn’t small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on verification with the records,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your identity has been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Law Enforcement Unit will send you to the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your return is just in time;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow happens to be the Inner Academy Qualifying Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year Ruo Lin registered you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but, unfortunately, you didn’t come,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,infuriating her to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I really couldn’t make it for certain reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am not concerned with matters between you and your instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Head on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Xun’er, wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Xun’er is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She actually defeated Mo Wen in such a short time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, she’s so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ve allowed me to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next round,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Xuan Level Class Three, Xue Beng
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,versus Huang Level Class Two, Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Has that Xiao Yan not arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he was absent at the last Inner Academy Qualifying Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yea,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,this kind of cowardly, irresponsible man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,how did he enter the eyes of Xun’er?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A timid little rat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is he worth so much of your concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Level Class Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
